## Behaviour Rules

- Every table row leading to a detail view: `cursor-pointer` + `hover:bg-[#E6F7F5]`
- All modals close when the overlay background is clicked
- All forms validate required fields before submit and show inline errors
- All data-fetching shows a skeleton, never a blank screen
- All empty lists show an icon, title, and subtitle
- All monetary values use ₦ and are comma-formatted
- All dates use Nigerian convention: "1 Mar 2025"
- Never use `alert()` — always use Toast
- Never use `console.log` in finished code
- Active nav item: gold left border + `bg-[#F0A520]/10`

