## What the Manager Can and Cannot Do

If you are ever about to build a form that lets the manager create a
complaint or invoice — stop. That is wrong. Refer back to this list.

| Action | Who |
|---|---|
| Create a complaint | ❌ AI only — never build this UI |
| Create an invoice | ❌ AI only — never build this UI |
| Send invoice to tenant | ❌ AI only — never build this UI |
| Send rent reminders | ❌ AI only — never build this UI |
| Send receipt to tenant | ❌ AI only — never build this UI |
| Approve a payment | ✅ Manager — build the Approvals UI |
| Query a payment | ✅ Manager — build the Query UI |
| Assign vendor to complaint | ✅ Manager — build the Assignment UI |
| Update complaint status | ✅ Manager — build the Status UI |
| Add property | ✅ Manager — build the modal |
| Add tenant | ✅ Manager — build the modal |
| Add vendor | ✅ Manager — build the modal |
| Send broadcast | ✅ Manager — build the Broadcast UI |
| Take over inbox thread | ✅ Manager — build the AI toggle |
| Log job cost | ✅ Manager — build the cost field |

