## Do Not

- Do not use inline styles — use Tailwind classes
- Do not build an Express server or any backend code
- Do not create a new component if a shared one already exists
- Do not build mobile layouts unless asked — desktop first
- Do not use placeholder lorem ipsum — use realistic Nigerian data
- Do not add animations beyond skeleton pulse and modal slide-in unless asked
- Do not skip loading and empty states
- Do not move to the next feature until the current one is reviewed

